	echnique over power\n\nSession structure:\n• Warm-up (8 min) — Passing int
	o space\, light touches\n• Technique block (15 min) — Static ball — placem
	ent corners\n• Movement finishes (15 min) — Receive-pass-shoot or dribble-
	cut-shoot\n• Pressure reps (10 min) — Time limit or consecutive goals\n• C
	ooldown (2 min) — Easy passes\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in ins
	tagram_drill_library.json or session_themes.json → shooting.instagramUrls\
	n\nTheme focus: striking technique\, placement\, off the dribble\, first-t
	ime finishes
